  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "In a large skillet, sauté the diced peppers in 2 tablespoons of olive oil until tender.",
    "In a separate bowl, mix the crushed biscuits, melted butter, and a pinch of salt.",
    "In a greased 9x13-inch baking dish, arrange half of the biscuit mixture.",
    "Add the sautéed peppers, crumbled bacon, and grated cheese on top.",
    "Top with the remaining biscuit mixture.",
